 ratio, gas fraction, and the non-universal molecular\ngas consumption timescale are all robust to a range of recent\nmetallicity-dependent CO/H2 conversion factors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Sep 2014 20:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
