es: a fast ($\\approx 500$ km~s$^{-1}$) sequence, driven by the\nunshocked free-wind; and a slow sequence ($\\approx \\pm 100$ km s$^{-1}$) at the\nconical interface of the superwind and the hot halo.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Sep 2014 06:19:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Jan 2015 12:09:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-13"}
