oducible pathway for the scaling up of quantum\nmechanical circuits operating at practical temperatures (~77 K) as well as an\navenue to conduct superconducting tunneling studies in HTS for basic science.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Sep 2014 06:32:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-18"}
